                     <interp inst="t17880402-19-off93" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               for stealing, on the <rs id="t17880402-19-cd94" type="crimeDate">6th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880402-19-off93 t17880402-19-cd94"></join>, one piece of silk handkerchiefs, containing<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178804020048"></xptr>six in number, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880402-19-victim264" type="victimName">
